quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  53,0,shuru allah ka naam le kar jo bara meharban nihayat reham wala hai
  53,1,tarre ki qasam jab gayab honay lagey
  53,2,ke tumahray Rafeeq ( Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihiwasallam ) nah rasta bhoolay hain nah bhatkay hain
  53,3,aur nah khwahish nafs se munh se baat nikaltay hain
  53,4,yeh ( quran ) to hukum khuda hai jo ( un ki taraf ) bheja jata hai
  53,5,un ko nihayat qowat walay ne sikhaya
  53,6,( yani Jibraiel ) taaqatwar ne phir woh poooray nazar aeye
  53,7,aur woh ( aasman ke ) ounchay kinare mein they
  53,8,phir qareeb hue aur aur agay barhay
  53,9,to do kamaan ke faaslay par ya is se bhi kam
  53,10,phir khuda ne apne bande ki taraf jo bheja so bheja
  53,11,jo kuch unhon ne dekha un ke dil ne is ko jhoot nah maana
  53,12,kiya jo kuch woh dekhte hain tum is mein un se jhagarte ho ?
  53,13,aur unhon ne is ko aik baar bhi dekha hai
  53,14,parli hadd ki berri ke paas
  53,15,isi ke paas rehne ki jannat hai
  53,16,jab ke is berry par chhaa raha tha jo chhaa raha tha
  53,17,un ki aankhh nah to aur taraf mael hui aur nah ( hadd se ) agay barhi
  53,18,unhon ne apne perwar-digaar ( ki qudrat ) ki kitni hi barri barri nishanain dekhen
  53,19,bhala tum logon ne laat aur uzzaa ko dekha
  53,20,aur teesray menat ko ( ke yeh buut kahin khuda ho saktay hain )
  53,21,( mushrako! )kiya tumahray liye to betay aur khuda ke liye betiyan
  53,22,yeh taqseem to bohat be insafi ki hai
  53,23,woh to sirf naam hi naam hain jo tum ne aur tumahray baap dada ne ghurr liye hain. khuda ne to un ki koi sanad nazil nahi ki. yeh log mehez zan ( fasid ) aur khwahisaat nafs ke peechay chal rahay hain. halaank un ke perwar-digaar ki taraf se un ke paas hadaayat aa chuki hai
  53,24,kiya jis cheez ki ensaan arzoo karta hai woh usay zaroor millti hai
  53,25,akhirat aur duniya to allah hi ke haath mein hai
  53,26,aur asmano mein bohat se farishtay hain jin ki sifarish kuch bhi faida nahi deti magar is waqt ke khuda jis ke liye chahay ijazat bakhshay aur ( sifarish ) pasand kere
  53,27,jo log akhirat par imaan nahi laatay woh firshton ko ( khuda ki ) larkiyon ke naam se mosoom karte hain
  53,28,halaank un ko is ki kuch khabar nahi. woh sirf zan par chaltay hain. aur zan yaqeen ke muqablay mein kuch kaam nahi aata
  53,29,to jo hamari yaad se rogrdani aur sirf duniya hi ki zindagi ka khwaahan ho is se tum bhi munh phair lau
  53,30,un ke ilm ki intahaa yahi hai. tumhara perwar-digaar is ko bhi khoob jaanta hai jo is ke raste se bhatak gaya aur is se bhi khoob waaqif hai jo raste par chala
  53,31,aur jo kuch asmano mein hai aur jo kuch zameen mein hai sab khuda hi ka hai ( aur is ne khalqat ko ) is liye ( pedakiya hai ) ke jin logon ne buray kaam kiye un ko un ke aamaal ka ( bura ) badla day aur jinhon ne naikian kee un ko naik badla day
  53,32,jo Saghira gunaaho ke siwa barray barray gunaaho aur be hiyai ki baton se ijtinab karte hain. be shak tumhara perwar-digaar barri bakhshish wala hai. woh tum ko khoob jaanta hai. jab is ne tum ko matti se pedakiya aur jab tum apni maaon ke pait mein bachay they. to apne aap ko pak saaf nah jatao. jo parhaizgaar hai woh is se khoob waaqif hai
  53,33,bhala tum ne is shakhs ko dekha jis ne munh phair liya
  53,34,aur thora sa diya ( phir ) haath rok liya
  53,35,kiya is ke paas ghaib ka ilm hai ke woh is ko dekh raha hai
  53,36,kiya jo baatein moose ke shifon mein hain un ki is ko khabar nahi pohanchi
  53,37,aur ibrahim ki jinhon ne ( haq taat o risaalat ) poora kiya
  53,38,yeh ke koi shakhs dosray ( ke gunah ) ka boojh nahi uthaye ga
  53,39,aur yeh ke ensaan ko wohi milta hai jis ki woh koshish karta hai
  53,40,aur yeh ke is ki koshish dekhi jaye gi
  53,41,phir is ko is ka poora poora badla diya jaye ga
  53,42,aur yeh ke tumahray perwar-digaar hi ke paas pohanchna hai
  53,43,aur yeh ke woh hansata aur rulaata hai
  53,44,aur yeh ke wohi maarta aur jalataa hai
  53,45,aur yeh ke wohi nar aur madah do qisam ( ke hewan ) peda karta hai
  53,46,( yani ) nutfay se jo ( reham mein ) dala jata hai
  53,47,aur yeh ke ( qayamat ko ) isi par dobarah uthana lazim hai
  53,48,aur yeh ke wohi doulat mand banata aur muflis karta hai
  53,49,aur yeh ke wohi sheri ka maalik hai
  53,50,aur yeh ke isi ne Aad awwal ko halaak kar dala
  53,51,aur smod ko bhi. gharz kisi ko baqi nah chorra
  53,52,aur un se pehlay qoum Nooh ko bhi. kuch shak nahi ke woh log barray hi zalim aur barray hi sarkash they
  53,53,aur isi ne ulti hui bustiyon ko day patka
  53,54,phir un par chaaya jo chaaya
  53,55,to ( ae ensaan ) to apne perwar-digaar ki kon si Nemat par jhagrre ga
  53,56,yeh ( Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihiwasallam ) bhi aglay dar sunanay walon mein se aik dar sunanay walay hain
  53,57,anay wali ( yani qayamat ) qareeb aa pohanchi
  53,58,is ( din ki tklifon ) ko khuda ke siwa koi daur nahi kar sakay ga
  53,59,ae munkareen khuda ) kiya tum is kalaam se taajjub karte ho ?
  53,60,aur hanstay ho aur rotay nahi ?
  53,61,aur tum ghaflat mein par rahay ho
  53,62,to khuda ke agay sajda karo aur ( isi ki ) ibadat karo
